573
00:55:41,440 --> 00:55:42,610
Prečo sa zabil?

574
00:55:43,980 --> 00:55:45,050
Neviem.

575
00:55:46,450 --> 00:55:49,820
Keby ste boli na mojom mieste,
vedeli by ste teraz prestať?

576
00:55:50,790 --> 00:55:52,990
Ak niečo chcem, vždy to dosiahnem.

577
00:56:03,330 --> 00:56:04,330
Samovražda...

578
00:56:07,100 --> 00:56:08,270
Jediné, čo viem je,

579
00:56:09,570 --> 00:56:11,270
